v1.0.1 - new crate and furnace loot!

General Changes:
+ Created GitHub for patch notes
+ Money cap increased to 50Qn

New Content:
+ A NEW Crate is now obtainable, you must discover it somewhere on the map!
+ Furnace Loot! Earn potions and crystals for FREE by processing ore! ...and maybe something better..
+ New Potion: Unbox Slot Potion (earn +1 unbox slot for 3 minutes!)
+ New Code: 'MOREUNBOXES'
+ Added the mysterious gate...
+ Added some admin abuse commands.. 

+ New tier of potions, that is EVEN STRONGER!
+ You can now purchase Crystals in the shop, and you can unlock a Crystalline dropper for purchasing the highest tier.
+ Potion Pack now contains all top tiers of potions and an Unbox Slot potion.

- Removed bugged items from player inventories.

QoL Changes:
+ New pop-up and effects for completing achievements, so you know when you're making progress.
+ You will now continue opening the last crate you opened when you rejoin.
+ Dropper stat info now shows Ore Size.
+ Added a pointer inventory for onboarding
+ Tooltip now appears on shop items.
+ Clear all button can now be found in settings (this will be in a nice place later)

- Hid the inspect button while it does not work (coming soon!)

New Settings:
+ Turn on/off ore values to reduce lag! [off = no ore values, minimal = every 10 ore, all = every ore ]

Bug Fixes:
+ Onboarding no longer covers top bar and ore limit
+ Sapphire Dropper is now a legendary item

Balance Changes:
+ Toxic Wasteland now has stats. It does 25x if 3+ effects, 12.5x otherwise.

PUSHED TO NEXT UPDATE:


QoL Changes:
+ Removed unobtainable items from the index.
+ Controls now appear on screen

+ New Inventory, more traditional format, like Miner's Haven.
+ Smarter search (search by tier, item type, name)

New Settings:
+ Toggle Advanced Filters On (sort by upgrade range, multiplier, shiny only, mythic only)
+ Big Secrets, turn on/off secrets appearing big in your inventory
